you what to do and what not to...

252
00:18:53,215 --> 00:18:54,258
You know what, Gilberto?

253
00:18:54,341 --> 00:18:58,762
Since you were a kid, you had a big
mouth. Why don't you just shut up?

254
00:18:59,263 --> 00:19:00,305
[BEEPS]

255
00:19:01,098 --> 00:19:03,100
He's fucking lost his mind.

256
00:19:03,851 --> 00:19:06,103
All these acts of violence
in the North Valley

257
00:19:06,186 --> 00:19:08,313
are straining our friends' patience.

258
00:19:08,397 --> 00:19:11,608
Any surrender deal's
hanging by a thread.

259
00:19:11,692 --> 00:19:13,527
Uncle Miguel has to see that.

260
00:19:13,610 --> 00:19:15,946
I told him, no violence.

261
00:19:17,281 --> 00:19:19,491
Is this all my fault?

262
00:19:20,117 --> 00:19:23,495
Haven't I always done
what was best for him?

263
00:19:26,748 --> 00:19:28,000
Franklin Jurado.

264
00:19:29,877 --> 00:19:32,713
I need to reach out to Chepe. Or Pacho.

265
00:19:33,255 --> 00:19:34,840
But how the fuck...?

266
00:19:35,174 --> 00:19:37,926
There's no one else I
can trust with this.

267
00:19:38,802 --> 00:19:39,803
Let's see...

268
00:19:42,806 --> 00:19:43,807
Dad.

269
00:19:54,651 --> 00:19:55,652
Nicolás...

270
00:19:57,946 --> 00:20:01,700
I need you to get involved
in the Jurado situation.

271
00:20:13,548 --> 00:20:14,620
Hello.

272
00:20:16,506 --> 00:20:17,549
Any news?

273
00:20:17,633 --> 00:20:19,801
He has a girlfriend on
the other side of town.

274
00:20:20,177 --> 00:20:24,932
Look, David, if Enrique was a rat,
he wouldn't be around anymore.

275
00:20:25,015 --> 00:20:27,142
Ah... Thanks.

276
00:20:27,851 --> 00:20:29,436
I think I'll wait here.

277
00:20:30,437 --> 00:20:33,607
You know he's a mama's boy.
That fucker will be back.

278
00:20:35,859 --> 00:20:36,944
So now what?

279
00:20:37,392 --> 00:20:38,396
[SIGHS]

280
00:20:38,403 --> 00:20:41,490
Now you go to Toro Negro.
Navegante's waiting for you.

281
00:20:41,573 --> 00:20:43,575
He'll give you an
assignment from my father.

282
00:20:45,160 --> 00:20:46,995
Why didn't he call me?

283
00:20:49,373 --> 00:20:51,124
I'm going to explain something to you.

284
00:20:51,208 --> 00:20:55,712
Until this is figured out,
you only talk to me. Understood?

285
00:20:57,673 --> 00:20:58,674
Yes, sir.

286
00:20:59,675 --> 00:21:05,180
Better get moving.
Navegante hates to wait.

287
00:21:16,316 --> 00:21:18,819
[ROCK MUSIC PLAYING]

288
00:21:25,534 --> 00:21:29,955
[MAN] Coming up to coordinates
Kirk 5-7, maneuver incoming.

289
00:21:30,038 --> 00:21:33,792
[ ENGLISH] Private militias not
