296
00:21:52,894 --> 00:21:55,314
Third generation night vision goggles.

297
00:21:55,814 --> 00:22:00,819
The same ones the Americans used
in Operation Desert Shield.

298
00:22:02,112 --> 00:22:07,451
Peña, can we keep them afterwards
as a contribution to the cause?

299
00:22:08,910 --> 00:22:12,539
[ENGLISH] The Castaños ran the
largest private militia in Colombia.

300
00:22:12,622 --> 00:22:16,960
Their AUC, or Autodefensas
Unidas de Colombia,

301
00:22:17,044 --> 00:22:19,004
