302
00:22:19,463 --> 00:22:22,299
Their victims...
in the hundreds of thousands.

303
00:22:23,175 --> 00:22:24,384
Theirs was a perpetual war.

304
00:22:25,135 --> 00:22:27,600
And if you're hunting communist
guerrillas in the jungle,

305
00:22:27,607 --> 00:22:28,944
they were your only call.

306
00:22:29,470 --> 00:22:30,499
[BLASTS]

307
00:22:30,515 --> 00:22:32,434
This one has AFCS.

308
00:22:33,268 --> 00:22:35,979
And the 701 engine. Hmm.

309
00:22:36,563 --> 00:22:37,773
[CHUCKLES]

