477
00:35:16,030 --> 00:35:17,740
Don't forget the suitcase.

478
00:35:18,574 --> 00:35:20,201
[COMMANDING OFFICER] Keep going!

479
00:35:20,284 --> 00:35:23,371
Come on. Let's go! Assume position!

480
00:35:23,454 --> 00:35:25,790
[HELICOPTER WHIRRING]

481
00:35:36,384 --> 00:35:39,470
[MAN] Be advised, team:
five minutes to LZ.

482
00:35:40,555 --> 00:35:43,224
[PEÑA BREATHING HEAVILY]

483
00:35:56,487 --> 00:35:59,115
[THUNDER RUMBLING]

484
00:36:35,943 --> 00:36:37,695
[VIBRATING]

485
00:36:38,112 --> 00:36:39,113
[BEEPS]

486
00:37:01,010 --> 00:37:03,387
Let's see how our new toys work.

487
00:37:06,766 --> 00:37:08,351
[POWERING UP]

488
00:37:08,976 --> 00:37:10,031
Get ready.

489
00:37:13,314 --> 00:37:15,066
[IN ENGLISH] God bless America.

490
00:37:36,545 --> 00:37:37,713
[GROANS]

491
00:37:40,841 --> 00:37:42,218
[SNIFFS]

492
00:37:48,849 --> 00:37:51,519
[IN SPANISH] Ah...
Our guest of honor's arrived.

493
00:37:52,520 --> 00:37:54,146
[COUGHS, BLOOD SPLATTERS]

494
00:37:55,815 --> 00:37:57,400
