495
00:38:01,570 --> 00:38:05,116
Jorge, you're going to have
to explain some things.

496
00:38:06,742 --> 00:38:08,536
[CRICKETS CHIRPING]

497
00:38:15,418 --> 00:38:17,211
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

498
00:38:20,506 --> 00:38:21,882
Alpha in position.

499
00:38:22,425 --> 00:38:24,010
[DAVID] Tell him what you told us.

500
00:38:26,595 --> 00:38:27,722
Huh?

501
00:38:27,805 --> 00:38:29,807
[ENRIQUE] Salcedo knew about the DEA.

502
00:38:30,641 --> 00:38:33,102
You're going to talk to me
like a man, motherfucker.

503
00:38:33,109 --> 00:38:34,138
[WINCES]

504
00:38:34,145 --> 00:38:35,730
[YELLS] Salcedo works with the DEA!

505
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:38,482
He knew the DEA was in Cali.

506
00:38:40,318 --> 00:38:43,446
He knew where they were at
